Each player gets five cards. 
put the extra cards in a deck in the center
ask a specific person for a specific numer/letter
if the person has the card of the number/letter:
  obtain all cards of the number/letter
 else if:
  obtain the top card from the cards deck
moving clockwise, the next player take their turns to ask for number/letters. 
If you are being asked and have the number/letter he/she asks for:
  give all cards of the same number/letters to the player
If you are being asked and do not have the number/letters he/she asks for:
  say "go fish"
if you encounter four cards of the same number or letter:
  lay the cards down flat on a surface and obtain a point
The person with the most points at the end of the game wins. 
